      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, presenting in concours-level condition with comprehensive service documentation. The S54 3.2L inline-six remains a masterpiece of atmospheric induction, featuring a recently overhauled VANOS system and updated rod bearings for total mechanical peace of mind. Power is delivered through a crisp ZF 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. The chassis is impeccable, with the rear subframe mounting points reinforced as a preventative measure. Suspension geometry remains factory-spec, utilizing fresh OEM bushings and dampers to preserve the legendary steering feedback. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its original matte finish with zero bolster wear. A true turn-key example for the discerning collector.",
